  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objectives of the trial of a medication-coach program for patients with stroke or
      transient ischemic attack are to pilot test the study design, the intervention components
      and the data collection forms and refine them for a larger trial whose goal will be to
      improve long-term adherence to stroke prevention medications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
